social_posts.post_text: Dreaming about riding through spring flowers
Far away in a day dream
Every day is different on the trail. Flowers change. Trees fall. Sometimes we meet snakes. But every day is an adventure.
In the spring, at the end of the day, you should smell like dirt
“I only went out for a walk, and finally concluded to stay out till sundown, for going out, I found, was really going in.”
Butterflies sunsets sweaty horses and wildflowers
Kissed by the sun, bitten by the moon
